* Requires JRuby, http://jruby.org/download
* RubyMine, add JRuby SDK: File > Settings > Ruby SDK and Gems > Add Ruby Interpreter > 
Find JRuby.exe, e.g. C:\Program Files\jruby-1.4.0\bin\jruby.exe
* Requires gems: rack, rack-test, rspec, sinatra, json-jruby. 
To install these under jruby: jruby -S gem install sinatra